OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783725539
OL,3,CItalian beaches booked until September
OL,4,Cas tourism weighs on beauty spots
OL,6,FPicturesque Italian regions struggling
OL,7,Fto deal with an onslaught of tourists
OL,8,Fhave resorted to booking systems for
OL,9,Ftheir limited beach space, but with
OL,10,Fdemand so high, some are fully booked
OL,11,Funtil the middle of September.
OL,13,FItaly has seen a tourist boom since
OL,14,Fthe pandemic, but many of the most
OL,15,Fpopular destinations are small
OL,16,Fhistorical towns with stunning scenes
OL,17,Fthat do not have the infrastructure to
OL,18,Fsupport the new wave of visitors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
