CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783725539
OL,3,CItalian beaches booked until September
OL,4,Cas tourism weighs on beauty spots
OL,6,FThe beauty of the beaches has also led
OL,7,Fto one of their biggest weaknesses:
OL,8,Fmany of them are tucked into cracks in
OL,9,Fcoves or are on small spits of land
OL,10,Fjutting out from the cliff, meaning
OL,11,Fthey may be great for a picture, but
OL,12,Fthey're severely limited in space.
OL,14,FIn Sardinia, the UNESCO-protected Cala
OL,15,FGoloritze beach has implemented a
OL,16,Fbooking system, where people can
OL,17,Freserve spots on the beach for groups
OL,18,Fof up to four people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
