PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783725539
OL,3,CItalian beaches booked until September
OL,4,Cas tourism weighs on beauty spots
OL,6,FThe beach is a small spit of land in a
OL,7,Fcove off the east coast of the
OL,8,FMediterranean island, but with limited
OL,9,Fspace, eager tourists may be
OL,10,Fdisappointed to learn it is fully
OL,11,Fbooked until September 13 just as the
OL,12,Ftourist season in Italy comes to an
OL,13,Fend.
OL,15,FSardina has become particularly fond
OL,16,Fof the tactic, with the Cala Mariolu
OL,17,Fbeach having a similar system, and
OL,18,Fonly 700 people are allowed on the
OL,19,Fbeach at one time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
