PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783725539
OL,3,CItalian beaches booked until September
OL,4,Cas tourism weighs on beauty spots
OL,6,FCala dei Gabbiani, also on the east
OL,7,Fcoast of the island, limits visitors
OL,8,Fto just an hour and a half per slot as
OL,9,Fthey seek to control tourist numbers.
OL,11,FSome local authorities have reserved
OL,12,Fpart of the beach for short-term
OL,13,Fbookings, up to three days in advance,
OL,14,Fbut these are snapped up fast.
OL,16,FAuthorities in Liguria and Sicily have
OL,17,Falso adopted similar booking systems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
