PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783725539
OL,3,CItalian beaches booked until September
OL,4,Cas tourism weighs on beauty spots
OL,6,FThe number of tourists visiting
OL,7,FItaly's beaches has also increased
OL,8,Fpressure on the local environment,
OL,9,Fwith coveted white beaches seeing
OL,10,Ftheir stock of sand slowly depleted as
OL,11,Fpeople kick it up when placing towels.
OL,13,FItaly has become well-versed in
OL,14,Fdealing with high tourist numbers in
OL,15,Frecent years and has implemented
OL,16,Fnumerous policies to control the
OL,17,Fcrowds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
